  "instructions": [
    "Rehydrate the dried cherries by soaking them in water for 30 minutes",
    "Drain and rinse the rehydrated cherries",
    "In a large bowl, combine the mixed greens, crunchy chickpeas, and rehydrated cherries",
    "Sprinkle the crumbly feta cheese and toasted almonds over the top of the salad",
    "Drizzle the lemon-tahini dressing over the salad and toss to combine",
    "Gently fold in the spherified lemon juice pearls",
    "Season the salad with salt and pepper to taste",
    "Cover and refrigerate the salad for at least 30 minutes to allow the flavors to meld"
